options.text:
**Room**: 
An enclosed space (e.g. bedrooms, living rooms, kitchen)

**Other structure**: 
Besides rooms, any other structures that are sprayable (e.g. bathrooms, toilets, passages, open-kitchens)

**Building**: 
One or more conjoined rooms

**Homestead**: 
A yard with one or more buildings

**Household**: 
A group of people who share the same home

**Head of household**: 
Any person responsible for the people who live in a household
